Package app.photos

Interface IGooglePhotosBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GooglePhotosBuilder
    public interface IGooglePhotosBuilder
    Just to try-out builder pattern. IGooglePhotosDownloader library must be created with exact specified parameters, to change parameters, create a different object IGooglePhotosBuilder
